Rajkot, Get ready to experience Hush Fuss like never before! ❤️
For the very first time, the most awaited fashion and lifestyle exhibition is coming to your city — bringing with it over 35+ curated designers, stunning real jewellery labels, luxe accessories, festive wear, and so much more ! 🌸

Discover, shop, and celebrate fashion in its most exciting form 🛍️

Mark your calendars - Rajkot is about to get stylish !
